<HEAD>Thousands of Muscovites Vent Anger over Privileged Elite</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: To UPDATE with Yeltsin comments from newspaper interview, SUB
final 5 grafs, 15-19, bgng: `Voting takes...' with 9 grafs bgng: `A British...'
